         <abstract id="aspace_5ff9c61e71f7ece25b3a418449cc9800">The Philip Nolan papers document his expeditions from Louisiana into Texas in the years 1791-1801 and the reaction of the Spanish governors of Texas and Nuevo Santander, including the trial of Nolan's men by the Spanish.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
            <persname identifier="http://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n50021346"
                      relator="col"
